                            <comment id="17307259" author="ancosen" created="Tue, 23 Mar 2021 17:31:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;For the moment I set the fix version to all the active branches, lets check.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17307742" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2021 10:29:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Its possible that its a bug in the concat function&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17307763" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2021 11:47:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes its a bug in jsonpath library and its concat function&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17307780" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2021 12:13:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Okay its a bug in jsonpath, reported in their issue tracker&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/json-path/JsonPath/issues/680&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/json-path/JsonPath/issues/680&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17307786" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2021 12:22:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do not use the concat function, its also not really documented on their website page (so you found it somewhere elsewhere)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17308054" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2021 17:44:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have added a WARN on the camel jsonpath documentation page about the concat function has a bug, with reference to this JIRA ticket.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is nothing we can do in Camel itself. There is a suggested workaround in the docs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
